Gg_killzone_day
By warflango and MashedChicken

Goal: Gun Game. Really sweet. 

Notes: This is a remade version of fy_killzone_day by MashedChicken made for gungame.

mp_flashlight MUST be set to 1 if you want to have any clue where you're going underground or in a base with all the lights off.

Good luck!
